<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; padding: 40px 60px; color: #000; }
        h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 16pt; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h2 { font-size: 14pt; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: justify; }
        .party-block { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .signature-section { margin-top: 60px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .signature-block { width: 45%; }
        .line { border-top: 1px solid black; margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .page-break { page-break-after: always; }
        ol { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>{{contract.type}}</h1>

    <div class="party-block">
        <p>This Agreement is made and entered into as of <strong>{{contract.date}}</strong>, by and between:</p>
        <p><strong>{{parties.client.name}}</strong>, with a principal place of business at {{parties.client.address}} ("Client"), and</p>
        <p><strong>{{parties.provider.name}}</strong>, with a principal place of business at {{parties.provider.address}} ("Service Provider").</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Scope of Services</h2>
    <p>The Service Provider agrees to perform the following services for the Client:</p>
    <ul>
        {{#each services}}
        <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Payment Terms</h2>
    <p>Client shall pay the Service Provider the total sum of <strong>{{payment.amount}}</strong>. Payment shall be made according to the following schedule:</p>
    <p>{{payment.schedule}}</p>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>3. Confidentiality</h2>
    <p>Both parties agree to keep all proprietary information exchanged during the term of this Agreement confidential and not to disclose it to any third party without prior written consent.</p>

    <h2>4. Termination</h2>
    <p>Either party may terminate this Agreement with {{terms.noticePeriod}} written notice. Upon termination, Client shall pay for all services rendered up to the date of termination.</p>

    <h2>5. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of {{terms.state}}.</p>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div><strong>{{parties.client.name}}</strong></div>
            <div>{{parties.client.signer}}</div>
            <div>Title: {{parties.client.title}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div><strong>{{parties.provider.name}}</strong></div>
            <div>{{parties.provider.signer}}</div>
            <div>Title: {{parties.provider.title}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
